//The Resume Builder project is a web application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to streamline the creation of professional resumes. This user-friendly tool empowers individuals to craft polished resumes with ease. The project incorporates an intuitive user interface designed with HTML for the structure, CSS for styling, and JavaScript for dynamic functionality.

Users can input their personal and professional information into the form fields, and the JavaScript code dynamically updates the resume preview in real-time. This interactive feature provides users with immediate feedback on how their resume will appear, encouraging a seamless editing experience. CSS is utilized to enhance the visual appeal of the resume, ensuring a clean and professional presentation.

Additionally, the project may include features such as customizable templates, font styles, and color schemes, allowing users to personalize their resumes to suit their preferences. The final output is a downloadable, well-formatted resume document that can be easily shared with potential employers.

In summary, the Resume Builder project leverages the power of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to provide a user-friendly platform for creating professional resumes, combining functionality with aesthetics to enhance the overall job application experience.
